727668f-a.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - Sanford Avenue
727668f-a.text:
Parsons Boulevard, at the N.E. corner of Sanford Avenue,
showing the Malcolm Graham Mansion of 1873, a frame structure.
It was known in 1891 as the Club House.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
